{"tid":1970264,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"2019年理大圍城的士司機接載FA時受傷","createTime":"2020-04-13T04:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T00:26:56.000Z","uid":352010,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"88b1e33915bd74c95973130b6677feb2666736f7","tid":1970264,"uid":352010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:38:29.000Z","msg":"本人於<strong>2019年11月18日約上午5:20在紅磡機利士南路與曲街交界處</strong>，駕駛的士接載一名年約25歲男性FA前往將軍澳時，因有需要而要下車時<strong>被相信來自催淚鎗的强大氣流沖至整個人仆低，左肩脫較</strong>。由於公司要求，本人便在上述乘客的急救及照顧下用慢速駛回將軍澳交更地。本人其後入急症室治療，至今尚未康復，左手仍未能完全活動。本人現考慮對有關當局索償，急請以上乘客電郵lcnpeterng@yahoo.com.hk與本人聯絡。謝謝。"},{"pid":"e8a420746a23b89be4e6bd35da9db55264208791","tid":1970264,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:39:13.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"523412f40055020d6e88e5571d48af1456b0b315","tid":1970264,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:42:46.000Z","msg":"P牌照推"},{"pid":"4c69ae017f092de63c47134cca4441afa1569ec8","tid":1970264,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:43:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fe21e7a8d8a0a44d6e056adbcf9bbb71dca6fde6","tid":1970264,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:44:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ad08e68356c2cdab5c1e301ec693e52da79ef8cb","tid":1970264,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dSt2qCP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdSt2qCP.gif&h=e1a504e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9ea1335625559621012e301b5bc82bf8fd24fdbe","tid":1970264,"uid":242956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:45:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cb7cf913944651c3fce063c153814adc5de7fdab","tid":1970264,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-13T04:49:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore